  "description": "subDiv [2,4,6,0] = divide by 3, 5, 7 — the Oskar Sala inharmonic stack. Subharmonics that form NO recognizable harmonic series with each other. Not a chord, not noise. What the original Trautonium used for the serpent, the snake-charmer, the alien. The preset the library has never had.",
